WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.920 --> 00:00:06.160
America!  Once you were a great

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:11.280
nation.  You respected the laws of God,

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:14.670
you protected the innocent,

00:00:14.670 --> 00:00:17.970
you upheld the family.

00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:21.380
What have your leaders

00:00:21.380 --> 00:00:25.080
done to you?   What have drugs

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:29.990
done to you?  What has immorality done 

00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:33.059
to you?  Do you have

00:00:33.059 --> 00:00:37.399
a future?  Why have you abandoned

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:42.079
the family?  Supernatural

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:47.710
evil has overcome you.  Look around you:

00:00:47.710 --> 00:00:52.770
Is there a supernatural solution?

00:00:52.770 --> 00:00:57.260
Can the Mother of God

00:00:57.260 --> 00:00:59.750
help you?

00:00:59.750 --> 00:01:05.900
What did Mary promise at Fatima?  Have you ever prayed

00:01:05.900 --> 00:01:11.790
Mary's Rosary?  What did the Angel say
to Mary?

00:01:11.790 --> 00:01:14.800
"Hail Mary,

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:18.400
full of grace."

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.490
Can Mary still save

00:01:21.490 --> 00:01:26.140
America?  Mary

00:01:26.140 --> 00:01:30.520
will help us to become once again a
nation

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:34.460
under God, a nation for the born

00:01:34.460 --> 00:01:37.550
and the unborn, a holy nation,

00:01:37.550 --> 00:01:42.260
a people set apart.

00:01:42.260 --> 00:01:45.440
Please join our Millions for Mary

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:49.470
Apostolate.  Millions of Hail Mary's

00:01:49.470 --> 00:01:52.680
can save America.

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:56.570
Jesus listens to his mother like no one

00:01:56.570 --> 00:02:01.570
else.  I have personally committed to
praying

00:02:01.570 --> 00:02:05.070
one rosary everyday for

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:08.890
America.  Please visit our new blog

00:02:08.890 --> 00:02:14.300
millionsformary.wordpress.com

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:16.740
and to make your commitment,

00:02:16.740 --> 00:02:21.000
just click on the link provided below.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:24.980
Never forget, a nation

00:02:24.980 --> 00:02:28.650
that prays together stays

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:30.330
together.

